lastfm.summary: A Day Van is a discontinued make of the Chevrolet Astro van. The first half of the music video shows footage of Captain Joseph Kittinger skydiving from the Excelsior III, a gondola raised by balloons to 102,800 feet as part of Project Excelsior (a series of record-breaking dives from high-altitude). Captain Kittinger fell for 4 minutes and 36 seconds, reaching a maximum speed of 614 mph before opening his parachute at 18,000 feet. Read more on Last.fm.
